data.description: This is the perfect end unit overlooking the pond. Open floorplan with plenty of natural sunlight. Functional kitchen with an abundance of cabinet space and pantry. The adjoining dining area overlooks the peaceful water. The spacious living room is a great space with a private patio entrance. Large primary bedroom has ceiling fan, wic and luxury bath offering a separate shower and tub and extended vanity. Second bedroom is across from hall bathroom. Large laundry is conveniently located.  New flooring in the main living areas, new central air conditioner, fresh paint, and updated light fixtures throughout. This is it!! Welcome home!!
